{
  "stem": "13251.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's hard for me to understand how-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] My-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My parents-- they-- they were not city people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't really know what was going on in the world.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We lived out in the sticks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Let's face it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And for someone who-- who would have been informed, they would have recognized and understood the threat.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it seemed like they would be the first to say, here, take them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, it's like some-- some parents threw babies out of trains, because they knew they're going to get killed.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they-- they were realistic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But-- but my parents-- they didn't know what was going on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And yet, that this young English girl was able to convince them to let go of kids.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[CRYING] And that's really weird.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That's really strange.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I guess that's why I'm alive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Shortly after that, I'll tell you all about-- I remember the trip.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I mean, it's like clear in my mind.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We will picked up in a black car.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "In those days, they were all black cars, I guess.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And there was this English lady that came with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And there was one little girl.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I haven't the faintest idea who she is-- about our age, maybe a year older, and my brother.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And that was all the passengers in that car.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we-- we drove off to Prague.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, yeah, I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got--",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
